These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, poker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, august
3 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, guinea-pig
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, iris
City: colone, paris, liverpool
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, aquamarine
House: modern, tower, cape-cod
 1. the modern house is the person who likes orange##1
 2. the cape-cod house is the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person playing poker is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person playing domino##2
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 5. the person who growsrose is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the modern house is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Game      | domino    | poker   | scrabble           |
| Birthday          | june       | august    | march         |
| Pet         | mouse    | guinea-pig  | dog        |
| Flower           | daffodil | rose   | iris      |
| City   | paris        | liverpool    | colone       |
| Color   | orange     | turquise  | aquamarine       |
| House         | modern     | tower | cape-cod |

