There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, blood-red
3 different games are played: whist, billiard, chess
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, june
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, iris
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the nurse##1
 3. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the bus##2
 5. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is the photographer##1
 9. the nurse is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | bus   | trike    | skateboard         |
| Cigar          | dunhill    | pall-mall | ritmeester          |
| Job   | photographer  | nurse  | security-guard     |
