 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who growsbegonia##2
 7. the person traveling to london is between the person who likes emerald and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the nigerian is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
10. the mexican is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
