.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, pilot, entrepreneur
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, tiparillo
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris, daisy
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, pepper, papaya
House: ranch-style, craftsman, modern
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, fuchsia
 1. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
 2. the pilot is in the middle##1
 3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the modern house is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is between the mechanic and the person eating pomegranate##2
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person who growsiris is the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the modern house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
11. the person who likes chestnut is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Job      | mechanic | pilot      | entrepreneur      |
| Cigar         | dannemann     | havana     | tiparillo  |
| Flower   | daisy | amaryllis  | iris |
| Food   | pepper  | papaya     | pomegranate |
| House           | ranch-style        | modern | craftsman     |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | chess | go   |
| Color     | black        | fuchsia        | chestnut   |

