.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: chess, poker, domino
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, april
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, goldfish
House: cape-cod, craftsman, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, chesssy, sunflower
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, light-blue
There are 3 different nationalities: american, malaysian, russian
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the russian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who growsbegonia and the craftsman house##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the wooden house and the owner of the goldfish##2
6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person playing poker##1
8. the american is on the left of the person playing domino##1
9. the person who growschesssy is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game      | chess      | poker      | domino       |
| Birthday          | september      | april    | october   |
| Pet         | goldfish    | guinea-pig     | horse     |
| House           | craftsman    | cape-cod | wooden   |
| Flower   | chesssy    | sunflower    | begonia       |
| Color         | light-blue | fuchsia      | grey    |
| Nationality     | malaysian       | american | russian |

