.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, japanese
City: marseilles, venice, new-york
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, green, red
3 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, goldfish
House: art-deco, craftsman, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, january
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, go
1. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes green##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the person traveling to venice is between the japanese and the person who likes lavender##2
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the indonesian is on the right of the craftsman house##1
8. the person playing whist is the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Nationality      | japanese       | indonesian     | colombian         |
| City          | marseilles     | venice      | new-york     |
| Color         | green | red    | lavender      |
| Pet   | dog   | lizard | goldfish    |
| House   | craftsman        | gothic-revival     | art-deco   |
| Birthday         | december     | november | january |
| Game     | scrabble     | go       | whist    |

