.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
House: futuristic, art-deco, cottage
City: nizza, colone, boston
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, video-games, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, disco, electronic
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, chestnut, orange
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, september, february
1. the futuristic house is the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is between the cottage house and the person who likes orange##2
4. the fan folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
9. the fan disco is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | art-deco    | futuristic       | cottage      |
| City          | nizza   | boston   | colone  |
| Hobby           | video-games  | photography | skydiving    |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | disco     | electronic  |
| Color           | orange     | fuchsia        | chestnut |
| Game         | backgammon | canasta   | monopoly  |
| Birthday     | september    | february     | july      |

 